On Fri, 28 Dec 2007, Rennie wrote:

> I am thinking more along the lines of 25 gallons and more.  I'd like to go
> more than 325 miles when needed.

As others have suggested, marine catalogs are probably the best bet.  They
have all sorts of configurations.  I'm partial to the poly tanks over the
aluminum, as they don't have corrosion problems.

For larger capacity, it might be a better idea to install two tanks rather
than finding one big one.
